<div id="content">
<div id="center">
<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; <a href="/cybercrime/cyberwarfare">Cyberwarfare</a></div><div class="auth-picture"><img src="https://www.securityweek.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/auth_story/pictures/picture-106.jpg" alt="" title="" width="68" height="80" class="imagecache imagecache-auth_story" /></div><h2 class="page-title">North Korea-Linked &#039;ScarCruft&#039; Adds Bluetooth Harvester to Toolkit</h2><div id="node-17707" class="node clear-block">
<div class="meta">
<div class="submitted">
<div>
 By <a href="/authors/eduard-kovacs">Eduard Kovacs</a> on May 13, 2019 </div>
<div style="margin-top:2px;"><div style="float: left; margin: 1px 0pt 0pt 5px;">
<script type="ceae97bb5df74122f14afb6e-text/javascript" src="https://platform.linkedin.com/in.js"></script><script type="in/share" data-counter="right"></script>
</div>
<div style="float: left; width: 70px;"><g:plusone size="medium" href="https://www.securityweek.com/north-korea-linked-scarcruft-adds-bluetooth-harvester-toolkit"></g:plusone><script type="ceae97bb5df74122f14afb6e-text/javascript">
